  11 Sep 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -radiant-0.8.2-r1.ebuild,
  -radiant-0.9.1-r2.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

  16 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  radiant-1.0.0_rc3-r1.ebuild:
  Update after Ruby packages move.

  14 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata.xml so that it's the same as most other packages.

*radiant-1.0.0_rc3-r1 (08 Dec 2011)

  08 Dec 2011; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +radiant-1.0.0_rc3-r1.ebuild, -radiant-1.0.0_rc3.ebuild,
  files/radiant-1.0.0_rc3-deps.patch:
  Version bump; add a dependency over the new revision of activesupport so that
  it actually works (and force a rebuild due to bundler).

*radiant-1.0.0_rc3 (05 Dec 2011)

  05 Dec 2011; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/radiant-1.0.0_rc3-deps.patch, +radiant-1.0.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Add an ebuild for the latest release candidate; I was unable to get 0.9.1 to
  work, and this one seem not to work with Rails 3 installed, but it can't
  hurt.. more.

*radiant-0.9.1-r3 (14 Aug 2010)

  14 Aug 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.9.1-r3.ebuild,
  files/radiant-0.9.1-unbundled.patch:
  Make sure migration works in the unbundled case, fixes bug 332119.

  13 Aug 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -radiant-0.8.1.ebuild,
  -radiant-0.8.2.ebuild, -radiant-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

*radiant-0.9.1-r2 (11 Aug 2010)

  11 Aug 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.9.1-r2.ebuild,
  +files/radiant-0.9.1-unbundled.patch:
  Fix radiant paths for unbundled rails, thanks to Daniel Bahrdt in bug
  332119. Further fixes to make the generator work in this case.

*radiant-0.9.1 (29 Jul 2010)

  29 Jul 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.9.1.ebuild:
