  bug fixes.

*radiant-0.6.3 (13 Oct 2007)

  13 Oct 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.6.3.ebuild:
  Version bump with lots of bug fixes

*radiant-0.6.2 (08 Jul 2007)

  08 Jul 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. Note that versions 0.6.x are not backwards compatible with
  0.5.x. If you are currently running an 0.5.x version using the gem this
  upgrade *will* break your site.

  04 Feb 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> radiant-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Add ~amd64 now that bluecloth and redcloth dependencies are also marked
  ~amd64.

